{"tid":339821,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[畢業生注意]！千其唔好去Simpxx Studio租袍同影相","createTime":"2017-07-29T11:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T15:22:59.000Z","uid":11600,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ee37e3fded110fef0e8b93c041b3af888cdb02","tid":339821,"uid":11600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:23:33.000Z","msg":"1. 呢個最離普！！間野會係你還袍既時候拖你按金，會同你講冇晒Cash，之後要你留銀行戶口過數比你，但佢遲遲都唔會過數，有苦主比佢拖左成幾個月，我都比佢拖左成個月。<br />\n<br />\n2. 間野啲service 垃圾，可以入錯第二個家庭相去相架到，之後同我講會係第二日整番個岩既親身送去我屋企樓下，但第二日會冇影。<br />\n<br />\n3. 間野得一個電話可以打，就係call center。無論問咩條友都係答唔知。發生咩事唔知，同事做過乜唔知，大佬！咁要個call center黎做咩呀！？點解我唔可以直接打去分店到問？<br />\n<br />\n4. 聽其他苦主講，租袍果陣間野會話幫你影畢業相仲會送5張相比你，但你上到去影完就會瘋狂sell你，sell到你覺得唔買佢package係好cheap咁！<br />\n<br />\n5. 買左最貴既plan，當初應承我兩至三個月就比到我，間垃圾過左成半年時間先比到個相薄我！<br />\n執相仲要質素參差，執相執到個樣假到爆，唔執好過執，認真！<br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲們有其他伏野歡迎補充！"},{"pid":"0bf9b84c453909dedf0530f74a5549059b7a0fef","tid":339821,"uid":39780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"推到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8255932740211f4f3ea5decd41ff33bb23955201","tid":339821,"uid":11600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f67f1847d93bafb6c69d0695ac41591d1859d13","tid":339821,"uid":11600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3261823782ee7993663a70d388e4bd9cfbd39ead","tid":339821,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl