袍差唔多3個月都未收到訂<br />\n已經打左過去幾次，次次都話會退會退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同朋友頂帽個角蝕左少少已經俾佢扣左150蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知係咪拎返黎果時已經爛左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初諗住租袍都係唔想買件袍返黎放屋企阻掟，點知俾佢左扣右扣<br />\n其他店買袍同佢租袍個價差唔多，勸大家寧願去第間買件袍影完掉左佢，都好過俾佢拖訂金幾個月仲要瘋狂扣你錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba70e94993c82f56589b535ebba8ca68f85b8a3","tid":339821,"uid":52957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40bd5ffb96a4998667e6dbcbbdaaf9bf164ee84","tid":339821,"uid":68972,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"千其唔好去Sxxpro Stxxxo到租 按金唔好諗住拎得番<br />\n上去追 間舖連$600都無 又話係會計部到, 負責人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06faf625f9914971b157b04f4ff9fd3ee594ed7e","tid":339821,"uid":32932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"之前訂左<br />\n個個fd都一肚氣<br />\n一時又話有袍，上到去又話冇<br />\n或者上到去拎幾粒鐘先拎到袍<br />\n<br />\nbook左studio影全家福<br />\n佢打黎改遲我booking一個鐘，之後個日同我講話冇改<br />\n搞到我地得勁少時間影相<br />\n<br />\n佢話或者可以第二日再黎過，我屌你啦<br />\n我exam period都專登係大西北出黎影，就係因為之後屋企人同我輪流唔係香港<br />\n<br />\n之後我唔係香港 屋企人去揀相，畀佢地sale到買左package<br />\n件袍quality係幾好，但係佢地啲服務真係垃圾級"},{"pid":"bee087e846bba2e09f343fc08a963edfbd3ffade","tid":339821,"uid":107860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T17:51:15.000Z","msg":"學校official要用呢間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過買左袍唔怕拎唔返訂<br />\n本身都有諗住book佢送嗰個影相package<br />\n因為唔係咁就唔會有機會全家齊人影一次相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係好怕俾人sell 又見到好多人講用佢package既不愉快經歷<br />\n所以就算啦 唔影啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22769f7881924c763dfe56cabfde187a1b019e2e","tid":339821,"uid":52957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}